    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.poster.avif?t=1737635374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.webm?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.mp4?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bananitro </strong>是一款2D跑酷游戏，结合了速度和动作，拥有独特的重力机制。获得了&quot;猴子大赛2024&quot;的奖项，<strong>Bananitro </strong>创新地将猴子和自行车结合在一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奔跑迎接胜利</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制猴子骑自行车，使用<strong>Bananitro </strong>来达到惊人的速度，爬墙、做特技、并进行挑战重力定律的华丽跳跃。但要小心，每条赛道都是独特的，并充满障碍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >释放你的创意</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要害怕以自己的风格奔跑。无论是快速而谨慎，还是大胆而无畏，或者完全即兴创作，在<strong>Bananitro</strong>中，创意是完成赛道的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras_big/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374 width=800 height=777 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
